    public final class HoneycombAsyncTaskExecInterface
extends java.lang.Object
implements AsyncTaskExecInterface
    On Honeycomb and later, AsyncTask returns to serial execution by default which is undesirable. This calls Honeycomb-only APIs to request parallel execution.
